Introduction

KEEMBO was a female duo under ARA-LINE. Consisted of former members of SPICA, Kim Boa and Kim Bohyung, they debuted on April 10, 2020 with the digital single "Thank You, Anyway".

Their name is made up from their last name, Kim, and the first syllable of their first name, Bo.

They are presumed to have disbanded some time around 2021 due to a lack of social media activity.
